## Actor

- id: {{ perspective.actor.id }}
- name: {{ perspective.actor.name }}
- description: {{ perspective.actor.description }}
- public state: {{ perspective.actor.public_state }}
- private state: {{ perspective.actor.private_state }}
- current activity: {{ perspective.actor.current_activity.name }}

## User input that prompted this response

{{ perspective.user_input }}

## Location

- id: {{ perspective.location.id }}
- name: {{ perspective.location.name }}
- description: {{ perspective.location.description }}

## Relevant inventory

{% for entry in perspective.inventory %}
- stack id: {{ entry.stack_id }}; item id: {{ entry.item_id }}; {{ entry.name }} x{{ entry.quantity }}; description: {{ entry.description }}{% if entry.quality %}; quality: {{ entry.quality }}{% endif %}
{% else %}
- none
{% endfor %}

## Perceived characters

{% for entry in perspective.perceived_characters %}
- id: {{ entry.character.id }}; name: {{ entry.character.name }}; state: {{ entry.character.public_state }}; affordances: {{ entry.affordances }}{% if entry.notes %}; notes: {{ entry.notes }}{% endif %}
{% else %}
- none
{% endfor %}

## Recalled memories

{% for entry in perspective.relevant_memories %}
- memory id: {{ entry.memory.id }}; summary: {{ entry.memory.summary }}; event: {{ entry.event_name }}; support: {{ entry.support_type }}; confidence: {{ entry.confidence }}; stance: {{ entry.stance }}
{% else %}
- none
{% endfor %}

## Original ActionProposal

{{ proposal }}

## Incomplete speak action

- label: {{ action.label }}
- target ids: {{ action.target_ids }}
- expected effects: {{ action.expected_effects }}
- required preconditions: {{ action.required_preconditions }}

## Proposal reasoning

{{ reasoning_summary }}

## Suggested memory updates

{% for update in memory_updates_suggested %}
- {{ update }}
{% else %}
- none
{% endfor %}

Return the spoken line only.
